history.content:
It might be more hassle than it's worth to try and waive out of 16A. I would say if you feel like you can do 61A/70 first semester, you can probably also do 61A/70/16A. 

Of course, there's no harm in starting off with all 3 and then dropping one before the drop deadline.

children.subject: I thought 16A seemed like a lot of unnecessary HW and lectures, that was all. Thanks then for the advice
